Package: apksearch
Version: 1.3.5
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: python, python-pip
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://abhithemodder.github.io/apksearch/
Description: APK Search Tool for Multiple APK Websites
 apksearch is a Python library designed to search for APK files on
 different APK websites, such as APKPure and APKMirror. It allows
 users to find APKs, check for available versions, and retrieve
 download links.
